&lt;h2 id=&#34;重点-2博客回国--cdn-加速&#34;&gt;重点 2：博客回国 + CDN 加速
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;既然有了合规域名那肯定是要干点什么的吧，就比如说是博客，没错，就是现在你看到的东西。最先博客是托管在国外 github 平台的，然后由于政策原因在国内打开很不稳定，现在备案之后可以使用&lt;strong&gt;国内 CDN 加速&lt;/strong&gt;，下面是效果图&lt;span class=&#34;stack-lazy-picture&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/83377c74dc65/a350205a5541/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/83377c74dc65/a350205a5541/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/83377c74dc65/a350205a5541/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/83377c74dc65/a350205a5541/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/83377c74dc65/a350205a5541/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/83377c74dc65/a350205a5541/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/83377c74dc65/a350205a5541/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/83377c74dc65/a350205a5541/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img
